<entry id="efesus" guid="5f62111b-c082-5786-ad80-1e7510d9ba41"><lexical-unit><form lang="id"><text>efesus</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="efesus_0" guid="dbdb15a0-953c-5a41-bae4-d094d25f9bd1"><grammatical-info value="Proper noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>Ephesians: The tenth book of the New Testament of the Bible, an epistle to the people of Ephesus which is attributed to Paul the Apostle</text></gloss></sense><sense id="efesus_1" guid="4d35c51c-3761-5e91-a0c4-def19d28c0af"><grammatical-info value="Proper noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>Ephesus (an ancient Greek city in Anatolia, near Selçuk in modern İzmir Province, Turkey)</text></gloss></sense></entry>
