<entry id="jaring" guid="46874a0d-019d-5f46-96fa-c65e00b428e0"><lexical-unit><form lang="id"><text>jaring</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="jaring_0" guid="329aa4bf-4d5a-544d-a272-66e0c5ca227a"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>net: a mesh of string, cord or rope</text></gloss></sense><sense id="jaring_1" guid="97c70eda-a8ee-5adf-a041-385051f4f7d1"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>a device made from such mesh, used for catching fish, butterflies, etc.; a device made from such mesh, generally used for trapping something</text></gloss></sense><sense id="jaring_2" guid="cc7858e2-ee2a-5e78-bb9e-155b1f628c02"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>a mesh stretched to divide the court in tennis, badminton, volleyball, etc.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="jaring_3" guid="1ca789c5-2fb6-508e-9dcf-db5ffb9c1161"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>a framework backed by a mesh, serving as the goal in hockey, soccer, lacrosse, etc.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="jaring_4" guid="54ce58b8-b081-5dba-b8b1-62a16559df29"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>trap</text></gloss></sense></entry>
