<entry id="kemungkinan" guid="a669120e-7acc-5777-81b4-59b7bb55f4a1"><lexical-unit><form lang="id"><text>kemungkinan</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="kemungkinan_0" guid="c6cadbbe-a70e-5ae9-8905-9217dcdb919f"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>possibility</text></gloss></sense><sense id="kemungkinan_1" guid="5f325ffb-aec6-5cfc-9289-b2966d435154"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>likelihood:</text></gloss></sense><sense id="kemungkinan_2" guid="56367b89-8e72-50b5-8497-79557f1b3996"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>the probability of a specified outcome; the chance of something happening; probability; the state or degree of being probable</text></gloss></sense><sense id="kemungkinan_3" guid="a862d706-ac75-544d-8623-0a778a31d79d"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>the probability that some fixed outcome was generated by a random distribution with a specific parameter</text></gloss></sense><sense id="kemungkinan_4" guid="68cc0bf0-b3e1-5bd3-892a-3493e8d46e35"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>odds: the ratio of the probability of an event happening to that of it not happening</text></gloss></sense></entry>
