<entry id="melibat" guid="9c8847cc-30f6-5cb8-be6d-f785e009a7ec"><lexical-unit><form lang="id"><text>melibat</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="melibat_0" guid="15611e32-531c-5d9f-a1dd-01addb2fce74"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to wrap up</text></gloss></sense><sense id="melibat_1" guid="2ef97663-ec0e-5e1f-8a6d-db1d4f8a6171"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to bandage, to dress (a wound).</text></gloss></sense><sense id="melibat_2" guid="6a55710d-b705-5815-a394-fe5d24feca6c"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to wind, to fold around.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="melibat_3" guid="a7d3c492-3e70-5202-8920-65e07d63cefb"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to involve in, to implicate in; to draw (into); to include (in).</text></gloss></sense></entry>
