<entry id="positif" guid="6af85b7a-e7ef-5c65-81a3-b74fe025483c"><lexical-unit><form lang="id"><text>positif</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="positif_0" guid="1b64bf11-c90f-5747-b5c6-31f15584286c"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>positive</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_1" guid="6a3712eb-cc34-5158-a0f7-92d0ae76c693"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>included, present, characterized by affirmation.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_2" guid="25aaf177-3ca0-5ab3-9555-e8224a730cab"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>fully assured in opinion.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_3" guid="29adab7d-15ba-5d3d-93f1-bc6a31eb9b4f"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>greater than zero.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_4" guid="ed456654-199b-584b-a065-66abba8fe4ea"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>having more protons than electrons.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_5" guid="9c8274e4-607e-59cd-8b2a-cc4aa45257fd"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>of a visual image, true to the original in light, shade and colour values.</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_6" guid="806418b7-cfa8-5aaf-a0e4-a6dd56fa252e"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>confirmed, straight-up</text></gloss></sense><sense id="positif_7" guid="109fc1c2-a6bf-5418-801a-9b497b9872e1"><grammatical-info value="Adjective"/><gloss lang="en"><text>characterized by the existence or presence of distinguishing qualities or features, rather than by their absence</text></gloss></sense></entry>
<entry id="pot" guid="55e56053-04da-553f-816c-107ccccebb0c"><lexical-unit><form lang="id"><text>pot</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="pot_0" guid="6b93ec62-11e9-55c4-8f29-821355b108d9"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>pot (a vessel used to hold soil for growing plants)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="pot_1" guid="d6edad7c-949e-5d5e-a1a7-8a2ef81ec831"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>ellipsis of pispot</text></gloss></sense><sense id="pot_2" guid="b32eec0c-47d2-5eca-80ba-827c757d2b8d"><grammatical-info value="Noun"/><gloss lang="en"><text>a variation of the marble game, played by at least two people, using a triangular image as a place for the marbles being bet on, played by the players</text></gloss></sense></entry>
